163
00:15:43,733 --> 00:15:44,865
Tidak.

164
00:16:11,893 --> 00:16:14,128
Jangan.

165
00:16:14,130 --> 00:16:15,563
Apa?

166
00:16:15,565 --> 00:16:17,231
