194
00:19:52,982 --> 00:19:54,715
Karena kau sudah mengendalikan diri.

195
00:19:54,717 --> 00:19:57,852
Karena urusan tak selesai
membuatku kesal.

196
00:20:00,555 --> 00:20:04,391
Jika aku tak bisa menjaga
kewarasanku...

197
00:20:04,393 --> 00:20:07,561
...itu karena hal buruk
selalu menimpaku...

198
00:20:07,563 --> 00:20:09,230
...tanpa henti.

199
00:20:09,232 --> 00:20:10,865
Pernah berhenti.
Saat ada pesta.

200
00:20:10,867 --> 00:20:12,333
